    "like_dislike_summary": {
      "pos_sentences": [
        "The course I joined was Electronics and Communication Engineering. I preferred this course because it consists of some of the best faculty, and good support is given to everyone.",
        "In my college, every student must do the internship because the head of the department is always thinking about the students lives. They do their best there, even though there is no stipend. However, the students gain knowledge and good experience.",
        "Companies such as Infosys, TCS, and HCL recruit here and offer every student the best packages within their ability.",
        "The fee structure is very good, and all of the students studies here are affordable with their own fees. There is also a JVD scholarship available for all students who secure a seat in college.",
        "Life will be awesome, and the gender ratio is like this: for every 2 boys, there are 4 girls. Yes, this ratio has been maintained for years, and it reflects good diversity and helps teach how to be in society.",
        "The hostel is very good with all facilities. There is a separate hostel for girls and boys. Good food is provided by the management with a maximum fee payment. The hostel is maintained in a disciplinary nature, and all students follow the rules and regulations.",
        "My college is the best in every aspect, but the lack of placement opportunities is a black mark."
      ],
      "neg_sentences": [
